LengYue Backend
===============

This repository contains code released under two distinct licenses.
The boundary is by directory and is documented below.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
Project root and all subdirectories EXCEPT `qeubo/`
------------------------------------------------------------------------

Released into the public domain under the Unlicense, per ADR-0006's
per-file header convention. The umbrella's licensing posture treats
every source file in `backend/` (outside `qeubo/`) as public domain.

This includes (non-exhaustive):
  - main.py, the api/ subpackage, core/, db/, domain/, repositories/,
    services/, schemas/.
  - All scripts under scripts/.
  - All shell scripts, configuration examples, and documentation
    under backend/.

